reviewText: This video is going to be a great Christmas present for my dad who served on the USS Sumner. My dad loves anything about his ship or the navy. This is something that he can use to reminisce about his time in the navy. This shows what it was like to live on these ships. I know he is going to love it!
I served on a Gearing class destroyer in the 60's, this is about what it was like then. It was not as bad as it looks.
